  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 : \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Legal Action Against Quota: Efforts of Diaspora Tamil Organisations",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Efforts have been made to initiate legal proceedings against the former president of Sri Lanka, Gotabaya Rajapaksa, in the courts of the United States, Britain, Canada and the International Court of Justice.",
        "Diaspora organizations working in the respective countries have entered the field in this process. At the same time, it is reported that some diaspora organizations are preparing to carry out the steps to set up an international court.",
        "While Gotabaya Rajapaksa is currently staying in Singapore, it is reported that he is taking steps to seek refuge in another country as the next step.",
        "In this situation, diaspora organizations in the United States, Britain, and Canada have intensified in taking legal action.",
        "In particular, these diaspora organizations have decided to bring international parties and carry out activities in the situation where he has lost the privileges seen to the president of a country and has been hated and driven away by the people of South Sri Lanka.",
        "In particular, it is reported that efforts have been made to file cases focusing on the crimes committed during the last war and the connection with the abducted and disappeared persons.",
        "However, it is learned that appropriate action will be taken if Gotabaya leaves Singapore."
      ],
